import React from 'react';
import {Button, FormControl, Input, TextField} from '@mui/material';

export default function form() {
  return (

      <FormControl>
          <TextField>

          <label>Nome:
              <Input  type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Sobrenome:
              <Input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>CPF:
              <Input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Promocoes:
              <Input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Novidades:
              <Input type="checkbox" />
          </label>

          <Button type="submit" variant="contained">Cadastrar</Button>
          </TextField>
      </FormControl>
  )
}
